product.title: Titan Forever Wings of Liberty Corp 2 Tee
product.body_html:
• Description
  • FAQ
  • Shipping

  • Are you a fan of Attack on Titan?

    Do you want to show your support for the brave soldiers who fight the monstrous titans? Then you need the Titan Forever Wings of Liberty Tee! This awesome shirt features the superior survey corps emblem and "Wings of Liberty" on the front. You'll feel the power and excitement of living in an apocalyptic world where humanity's fate hangs in the balance.

    Whether you're watching the anime, reading the manga, or playing the games, you'll love wearing this shirt and expressing your passion for Attack on Titan. Order yours today and free yourself of the destruction!

    Available in six different sizes, measurements are shown below. We always recommend choosing 1-2 sizes larger and comparing the measurements in the sizing chart to a tee that fits you.

    Size (inches) S M L XL XXL XXXL
    Bust 34 35 36 37 39 41
    Length (inches) 23 23 24 25 26 27
                 
    Size (cm) S M L XL XXL XXXL
    Bust 88 90 92 96 100 104
    Length      (cm) 58 60 62 64 66 68

    If you are interested in more items like this, please check out our website www.kawaiies.com


    Features

    🍙 Made with Modal and Premium Polyester
    🍙 Short oversized sleeves
    🍙 Design printed on the front


    Measurements may be off by 1-5cm for rounding up to a whole number.

  • Please follow the washing labels when cleaning the garment:

     Max temperature 30c, or cold water. Reverse garment to protect the print.

     Do not bleach

     Dry by the sun or hang it to dry. 

     Dry cleaning

     

  • FREE Tracked Shipping to the United States, Canada, United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, Spain, France, Italy, Austria, Netherlands, and many more. Find out more here: Shipping Policy.

    Packaging time: 1-3 Business days

    Shipping time: Est 5-30 Business days
